        This is a brief but thorough overview of the Psionicist Guild
aimed primarily at those interested in joining, but containing
information for those simply curious as well.
        While mages harness the power of magic, Druids that of Nature,
Clerics act as agents of the Divine, and Necromancers of Darkness, the
Psionicist utilizes the power of his own mind.  Psionicists' power comes
from within themselves and is developed and expanded through exploring
an individual's inner potential.  This makes it hard to classify what
the focus of the guild is.  There are many directions open and each
member chooses a different combination of abilities to develop.  Some
specialize in aiding others, some in the social aspects of expanded
communication, some in avoiding combat and obstacles, others in smiting
their enemies with mightly telepathic and/or telekinetic blows.  The
powers of the mind are wondrous and diverse.
 
 
